<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.6">
<l>tīrtta ṉulakaḷanta cēvaṭimēl pūntāmañ</l>
<l>cērtti yavaiyē civaṉmuṭimē ṟāṉkaṇṭu</l>
<l>pārttaṉ ṟeḷintoḻinta paintuḻāyaṉ perumai</l>
<l>pērttu moruvarāl pēcak kiṭantatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it possible for someone  again to speak</l>
<l>of the greatness of the one with fresh Tulsi who stopped being understood by the one who looked on,</l>
<l>seeing for himself on Śiva’s crown the flower strands</l>
<l>he had joined to the red feet that had measured the world of the saviour.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
